  *Notation:*  
  *---------*  
  *h - hammer*  
  *p - pulloff*  
  *~~~ - vibrato*  
  *^ - indicates bend (and always followed by a number in parenthenses to*  
      *show the step of the bend)*  
  */ - slide up*  
  *\ - slide down*  
  *4(5)~~~ - trill (here,we would trill between the 4th and 5th fret)*  
  *A.H. - artificial harmonics*  
  *N.H. - natural harmonics*  
  *P.M. - palm mute*  
  
